    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We’ll catch the broken thread again,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And finish what we here began;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "God will the mysteries explain,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And then, ah, then, we’ll understand."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Then trust in God through all thy days;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Fear not, for He doth hold thy hand;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Though dark thy way, still sing and praise,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Sometime, sometime, we’ll understand."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We’ll know why clouds instead of sun"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Were over many a cherished plan;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Why song has ceased when scarce begun;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "’Tis then, sometime, we’ll understand."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
