            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Why what we long for most of all,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Eludes so oft our eager hand;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Why hopes are crushed and castles fall,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Till then, sometime, we’ll understand."
            }
          ]
        }
